name: Mistoon_Emerald
description:
IMPORTANT NOTICE:

Hello everyone! Lately in the comments I have often seen people complaining that my LoRA are similar to each other or are not representative of the style they should represent. My models are not trained on material from other artists, and it is therefore difficult to explain what the actual output should be. Since preparing the material necessary for the publication of a LoRA usually takes me a day's work, I have therefore decided not to post all my LoRAs on CivitAI anymore, but from today I will only post those that I consider interesting enough for the audience of this site. If you are interested in downloading the other LoRA as well, you will find them all for FREE (and they'll always be) on my Patreon page (subscribers will have early access to each of these). Thank you all for your support!

I've started a community on Deviant Art to share images made with my models/LoRAs! Join here if you are interested!

IF YOU ARE NEW TO STABLE DIFFUSION OR YOU HAVE PROBLEMS WITH MY MODELS, GO HERE: Guide

What's new in V2?

Emerald is my least downloaded checkpoint and personal least favorite. It was too focused on a single style, and all the characters were really similar to each other. For V2 I've rebuilt the dataset from scratch using a custom LoRA trained on the pictures I liked from the previous iteration and adding an unreleased LoRA to make it more vibrant. The result is a more flexible model with less over saturated colors and easier to use with higher CFG values.

How to use this

If you are new to the world of Stable Diffusion, you can learn how to run it by yourself here:

Tutorial

You'll also need a VAE to use this. For the examples, I've used the Grapefruit one:

https://huggingface.co/iZELX1/Grapefruit/resolve/main/Grapefruit.vae.pt

What's this model

Mistoon_Emerald is a variant of my SD model Mistoon_Anime that tries to achieve a more "fan art cartoon" style while still maintaining some resemblance to the modern anime style.

The starting point for this model was my blend. From there, I then added a few of my custom LoRAs in the mix to change the esthetic.

Try also the other flavors:

The style

It creates realistic and expressive characters with a "cartoony" twist. Unlike other anime models that tend to have muted or dark colors, Mistoon_Emerald uses bright and vibrant colors to make the characters stand out.

All the examples have been created using this version of the model using my workflow. Check the guide if you want to learn more about my workflow.

The model can also easily do NSFW stuff (check the last examples).

I highly suggest using a low CFG (3-5) value to avoid the usual burn effect.

Guides

Learn how to create pictures like mine with my step-by-step tutorials:

  • Beginner's Guide

  • Prompting

  • High Resolution

  • Inpainting

  • ControlNet

  • My Workflow

Support My Work

Check out my Patreon for exclusive content:

https://www.patreon.com/Inzaniak

Do you want a custom LoRA or picture? Check out my commission page:

LoRA and Picture Commissions

If you want to support my work for free, you can also check out my music/art here:

  • Bandcamp

  • Instagram
